                <h2>Privacy Policy</h2>
                <p><strong>Last Updated:</strong> February 20, 2026</p>
                <hr>

                <p>
                    By using SWGoHBot ("the Bot"), you agree to this Privacy Policy. This policy explains what information we collect, how we use it, how long we keep it, and your rights regarding your data.
                </p>

                <h3>What Information We Collect</h3>

                <h4>Information from All Users</h4>
                <p>When you use the Bot, we collect:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Discord User ID:</strong> Your unique Discord identifier, used to save your preferences and provide personalized features</li>
                    <li><strong>Player Ally Code:</strong> Your Star Wars Galaxy of Heroes ally code, used to fetch your game data</li>
                    <li><strong>Server/Guild IDs:</strong> Discord server identifiers where the Bot is used, for guild-specific features and settings</li>
                    <li><strong>User Preferences:</strong> Settings you configure, notification preferences, and display options</li>
                    <li><strong>Command Usage Data:</strong> Information about which commands you use, to help us improve the Bot</li>
                </ul>

                <h4>Additional Information from Patreon Subscribers</h4>
                <p>If you subscribe to premium features via Patreon, we also collect:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Patreon ID:</strong> Your unique Patreon identifier</li>
                    <li><strong>Discord ID:</strong> Your Discord identifier, used to verify your Patreon subscription</li>
                </ul>
                <p>
                    This additional information is collected from the Patreon API to verify your subscription status and provide premium features. Patreon handles all payment processing—we do not store credit card information.
                </p>

                <h3>How We Use Your Information</h3>
                <p>We use the information we collect to:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Provide Bot Functionality:</strong> Character lookups, guild searching, arena tracking, and other core features</li>
                    <li><strong>Save Your Preferences:</strong> Remember your settings across sessions and servers</li>
                    <li><strong>Deliver Premium Features:</strong> Provide arena alerts and other Patreon-exclusive features to subscribers</li>
                    <li><strong>Improve the Service:</strong> Analyze command usage to understand which features are most valuable and identify areas for improvement</li>
                    <li><strong>Verify Subscriptions:</strong> Confirm Patreon subscription status for premium feature access</li>
                </ul>
                <p>
                    We fetch your public game data from EA's servers using the ally codes you provide. Your Discord information is not shared with EA or any other third parties.
                </p>

                <h3>How Long We Keep Your Information</h3>
                <p>Different types of data are retained for different periods:</p>

                <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 20px 0;">
